{"tid":265822,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"羅馬宣佈續約迪羅斯兩年","createTime":"2017-06-01T03:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-01T05:53:34.000Z","uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1eba9e216e55fdb2193a52e972a03bfadb1bc19b","tid":265822,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:26:19.000Z","msg":"香港時間5月31日，意甲勁旅羅馬官方宣佈，球隊和隊長德羅斯續約至2019年，屆時德羅斯將年滿36歲，很可能在這裡退役。<br />\n<br />\n　　德羅斯出自羅馬青訓，自2001年代表羅馬上演職業生涯首戰以來，已經為這裡服役16年，共出場561次攻入59球，他和托迪都是羅馬城的象徵。<br />\n<br />\n　　<span style=\"color: red;\">由於托迪剛剛告別羅馬，已經33歲的德羅斯將在下季出任羅馬正隊長</span>，雖然此前有傳聞稱德羅斯可能和托迪一起離開，但是最終他選擇留下。<br />\n<br />\n　　如果德羅斯履行完這份合約，他將年滿36歲，很可能完成一生一隊的壯舉。"},{"pid":"86bfa6d5b77f8378d9dd2e5440260c4339808b89","tid":265822,"uid":34490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:27:15.000Z","msg":"登基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207846bad92803cf30d29fecad45de67e5f331f2","tid":265822,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:27:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>登基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf58b8d510ad3fbf1a3ecd148de83233a653658","tid":265822,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:48:44.000Z","msg":"踢到40歲"},{"pid":"52eddf532bba9cb16c080fc20a646e22831f0fed","tid":265822,"uid":91875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 1 club man!型到爆!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8343e86b0f220277654a500b2de9aa4578b2a02c","tid":265822,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T03:54:23.000Z","msg":"終於做隊長"},{"pid":"72202c0304aa59d7c8c598756636f4d850cdb8c6","tid":265822,"uid":73748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,